- X Followers
- Posts Per Hour
- KOL Involvement: List or "None"

**Actionable Guidance:**
- If Buying: Position size, entry strategy, profit targets
- If Avoiding: Reason, alternative suggestions

**Flag Summary:**
- All Red Flags (bulleted list)
- All Green Flags (bulleted list)

